  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/219830/extras/ddf1d3e2a9369205d23bb5222f9c19c5.poster.avif?t=1756567409\" width=270 height=90 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/219830/extras/ddf1d3e2a9369205d23bb5222f9c19c5.webm?t=1756567409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/219830/extras/ddf1d3e2a9369205d23bb5222f9c19c5.mp4?t=1756567409\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  .  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/219830/extras/7b743ba35c9bbbca75a808395b755238.poster.avif?t=1756567409\" width=270 height=90 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/219830/extras/7b743ba35c9bbbca75a808395b755238.webm?t=1756567409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/219830/extras/7b743ba35c9bbbca75a808395b755238.mp4?t=1756567409\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>A few things you can do in King Arthur's Gold...<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Ultimate Medieval Build n`Kill Multiplayer Game with Destructible Environments </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>DESTROY </strong>the enemy castles with physics and explosives<br></li><li> <strong>BUILD </strong>Defenses With Freeform Building<br></li><li> Use the environment to <strong>BURN </strong>or drown enemies<br></li><li> <strong>DRIVE </strong>siege machines with your teammates<br></li><li> Freedom to run, board ships, <strong>DIG </strong>tunnels or fly in the air<br></li><li> Interact with a <strong>LIVING </strong>animal and plant world<br></li><li> <strong>FIGHT </strong>with 32 unpredictable humans in multiplayer<br></li><li> Singleplayer, cooperative and competitive game <strong>MODES</strong><br></li><li> <strong>CUSTOMIZE </strong>with 60+ unique heads<br></li><li> <strong>CREATE </strong>your own adventure with community created mods & scripts</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/219830/extras/debf893afab2d05e2ce8e9d38b310f70.poster.avif?t=1756567409\" width=270 height=90 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/219830/extras/debf893afab2d05e2ce8e9d38b310f70.webm?t=1756567409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/219830/extras/debf893afab2d05e2ce8e9d38b310f70.mp4?t=1756567409\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>King Arthur's Gold blends the cooperative aspects of <i>Lost Vikings</i>, mashes them with the full destructibility of <i>Worms</i> and the visual style and action of <i>Metal Slug</i>, brought to you by the creators of <i>Soldat</i>.",
